The blueprints pages all feature a page properties macro - but the index doesn't contain a page properties macro report.

This makes the page properties macro redundant, and is confusing for customers who would expect it to do something and may feel like they don't have a proper grasp of how the blueprints work.

We should therefore add some information in - maybe some placeholder text so that customers realise what it's for and what it does. For the blank ones, we should add in some relevant fields so they're more useful.

