Just started using 5.9.11 and I noticed two changes when working with attachments:

1. When inserting a new file, files are listed as miniatures now instead of lists of files as before. This makes hard to locate files on my case since filenames are long and the miniatures are not useful for compressed files. Having the option to disable miniatures (either per user or per space) would be great.

2. Files are inserted by default as miniatures even when the miniature cannot be rendered given the file format. It would be great if files whose miniatures cannot be rendered were inserted as links directly.

